title: Lunchbox Buys Major Country Artist’s Groceries + Bobby’s Boss Wants Him To Take Some Time Off

description:
Lunchbox talks about buying a major country artist’s groceries after they forgot their wallet. Bobby’s boss is suggesting he takes time off of work. Also, Eddie gives an update on his foster kids and how he feels about adoption.
